          {
            "question": "Is my personal story private?",
            "answer": "Yes. All prayer requests and personal stories are treated with strict confidentiality."
          },
          {
            "question": "What if I don't like the result?",
            "answer": "We offer a 100% satisfaction guarantee. If it doesn't bless you, we'll make it right."
          },
          {
            "question": "How long does it take to receive the video?",
            "answer": "Your finished video is delivered in just 2-5 minutes. We use advanced AI technology to create your personalized video quickly while maintaining the highest quality."
          },
          {
            "question": "What themes can I create videos about?",
            "answer": "Anything that honors God: birthdays, anniversaries, weddings, grief, encouragement, testimonies, or prayers for strength and healing. Share your heart, and we'll create a video that speaks to it."
          },
          {
            "question": "How will I receive the finished video?",
            "answer": "You will receive a secure link via email to play your video on any device and to easily share it with family and friends."
          },
          {
            "question": "Can I use the video at church or events?",
            "answer": "Yes, you may share and play your video at private events and church gatherings to inspire and comfort others."
          }
        ],
